    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Left lower dentitions of Scotoecus in occlusal view. A, S. albofuscus (AMNH 241054); B, S. olduvensis, n. sp. (NMT.004/Bat, Holotype, cast); C, S. hindei (AMNH 241055)." ;
